name: Deville Flamming Marbou Rosette headband/ or clip
description:
This is the wild/glam child of my collection. She is constructed of the finest materials. A pink satin rosette accompanies a black and white damask rosette. A flamming cluster of peacock feathers and marbou have been added for that special touch. Rhinestones caress the very tops of this silky satin rosette. This makes the perfect gift and is absolutely astonishing for portraits. Wonderful photography prop. Give your little one that little extra pizzaz that her wardrobe has been missing! More over this is a beautiful piece for an ultra chic adult looking for a night on the town or even weddings.
